Issue Reference: #56

## Checklist

- [x] Build the view and update the view model.
- [x] Create and maintain the states for the various sub-menus present in the menu.
- [x] Add the required data in the monitor to be fetched by the view.
- [x] Establish the communication between monitor and view to enable updating of the Context API.
- [x] Implement auto-hide of the menu dock following the inactivity in its surroundings.
- [x] Finalize the design of the Menu Section and update the view accordingly.
